00:00:31.940 --> 00:00:35.740
For those who somehow don't know, 
America has five ratings for films:

00:00:35.740 --> 00:00:37.980
"G", for General Audiences of all ages;

00:00:37.980 --> 00:00:40.220
"PG", for Parental Guidance suggested;

