00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:54.000
It doesn't sound like a bad system, except when you ask the question:

00:00:54.080 --> 00:00:55.580
"How is this...

00:00:55.740 --> 00:00:58.060
[screaming]

00:00:58.060 --> 00:00:59.700
